CHAVEZ v. UNITED STATES. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Eighth Circuit. February 15, 1915.) No. 4410. In Error to the District Court of the United States for the District of New Mexico. S. Burkhart, U. S. Atty., of Albuquerque, N. M., for the United States.

Before SANBORN and ADAMS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Writ of error docketed and dismissed, pursuant to rule 16, without costs to either party in this court, on motion of defendant in error.
